message:
feat: support plugin config for all LCM settings

Three-tier config precedence: env vars > plugin config > defaults.

Previously, configSchema.parse only read 'enabled' from the plugin
config object — all other settings (contextThreshold, freshTailCount,
incrementalMaxDepth, etc.) were silently ignored and only worked via
environment variables.

Now all LcmConfig fields can be set in plugins.entries.lossless-claw.config:

